"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"makes you develop an incredibly robust build to such extent that you would "
"not be allowed to compete in pre-Cataclysm sports."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。這一種會使你發展出極其健壯的體格，以至於你將不被允許參加大災變前的體育競賽。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Tough serum"
msgid_plural "Tough serums"
msgstr[0] "堅韌血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tough serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"hardens your bones and muscles, increasing the amount of hits you can take."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。這一種會強化你的骨骼和肌肉，增加你能承受的攻擊次數。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Durability serum"
msgid_plural "Durability serums"
msgstr[0] "耐久血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Durability serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"further enhances your body's durability beyond simple toughness."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。這一種會進一步增強你身體的耐久性，超越單純的堅韌。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Unbreakable serum"
msgid_plural "Unbreakable serums"
msgstr[0] "不破血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Unbreakable serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Basically "
"super soldier body durability."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。基本上就是超級士兵的身體耐久性。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Thick skin serum"
msgid_plural "Thick skin serums"
msgstr[0] "厚皮血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Thick skin serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. It "
"thickens your skin and gives you some resistance to being cut."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會增厚你的皮膚，並賦予你一些對切割傷害的抵抗力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Strong back serum"
msgid_plural "Strong back serums"
msgstr[0] "強背血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Strong back serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. With this "
"your spine reinforces itself and you become capable of carrying heavier "
"loads."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。使用後，你的脊柱會自我強化，使你能夠承載更重的負荷。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Strong stomach serum"
msgid_plural "Strong stomach serums"
msgstr[0] "強胃血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Strong stomach serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"fortitude of digestive systems."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。增強消化系統的堅韌性。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Deftness serum"
msgid_plural "Deftness serums"
msgstr[0] "靈巧血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Deftness serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Improves "
"recovery from attacks that didn't connect with a target via an increased "
"fight response reflex."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。通過增強戰鬥反應反射，改善從未能命中目標的攻擊中恢復的能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Substance tolerance serum"
msgid_plural "Substance tolerance serums"
msgstr[0] "物質耐受血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Substance tolerance serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Improves "
"your body's filtration of intoxicants."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。改善你身體對麻醉劑的過濾能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Gourmand serum"
msgid_plural "Gourmand serums"
msgstr[0] "美食家血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gourmand serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"dopamine production in response to ingesting good-tasting foods and expands "
"digestive system to accomodate more volume."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。增加攝入美味食物時多巴胺的分泌，並擴展消化系統以容納更多食物。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Addiction resistance serum"
msgid_plural "Addiction resistance serums"
msgstr[0] "成癮抗性血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Addiction resistance serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Lowers the"
" brain's reliance on external dopamine sources, effectively increasing "
"resistance to addictions."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。降低大腦對外部多巴胺來源的依賴，有效增加對成癮的抵抗力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Animal empathy serum"
msgid_plural "Animal empathy serums"
msgstr[0] "動物共情血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Animal empathy serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Inserts an"
" instinctual movement pattern that activates in the presence of animals into"
" your brain that makes animals less skittish or untrustworthy of you."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會在你的大腦中植入一種在動物面前激活的本能運動模式，使動物對你減少警惕或不信任。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Animal kinship serum"
msgid_plural "Animal kinship serums"
msgstr[0] "動物親和血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Animal kinship serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Rewrites "
"certain parts of your brain to make you move in the presence of animals in "
"such a way that makes most animals leave you alone or be curious enough that"
" they act in a friendly manner to check you out."
msgstr ""
"一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會重寫你大腦的某些部分，使你在動物面前以某種方式移動，讓大多數動物對你置之不理或產生足夠的好奇心，從而以友好的方式接近你。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Terrifier serum"
msgid_plural "Terrifier serums"
msgstr[0] "恐嚇者血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Terrifier serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Modifies "
"your pheromones and the way you carry yourself to instill fear into the "
"minds of creatures, making them more likely to flee or be intimidated."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會修改你的信息素和舉止方式，將恐懼植入生物的意識中，使它們更可能逃跑或被震懾。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Disease resistance serum"
msgid_plural "Disease resistance serums"
msgstr[0] "疾病抗性血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Disease resistance serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Enhances "
"your immune system against diseases."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它能增強你的免疫系統以抵抗疾病。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Adrenaline serum"
msgid_plural "Adrenaline serums"
msgstr[0] "腎上腺素血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Adrenaline serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"the response and size of adrenal glands."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它能增加腎上腺的反應能力和大小。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Less sleep serum"
msgid_plural "Less sleep serums"
msgstr[0] "少眠血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Less sleep serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Lessens "
"your body's reliance on sleep."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它能減少你身體對睡眠的依賴。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Self awareness serum"
msgid_plural "Self awareness serums"
msgstr[0] "自我感知血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Self awareness serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"your awareness on your body's state of being."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它能增強你對自身身體狀態的感知能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Masochism serum"
msgid_plural "Masochism serums"
msgstr[0] "受虐狂血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Masochism serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Rewrites "
"your brain to associate pain with pleasure."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會重寫你的大腦，將痛苦與愉悅聯繫起來。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Lighter steps serum"
msgid_plural "Lighter steps serums"
msgstr[0] "輕盈步伐血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lighter steps serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Changes "
"your movement patterns to make less noise while walking and lessens the "
"chance of triggering traps."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會改變你的移動模式，使行走時發出更少的噪音，並降低觸發陷阱的幾率。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Robust genetics serum"
msgid_plural "Robust genetics serums"
msgstr[0] "強健基因血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Robust genetics serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. "
"Supplements your DNA with buffers against damage and degeneration. Works "
"only with old mutations mod"
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會為你的DNA補充緩衝機制，以抵抗損傷和退化。僅適用於舊版突變模組。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Scout serum"
msgid_plural "Scout serums"
msgstr[0] "偵察兵血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Scout serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"your sight range and allows you to see distant things better."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它能增加你的視野範圍，並讓你更好地看清遠處的事物。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Cannibalism serum"
msgid_plural "Cannibalism serums"
msgstr[0] "食人血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cannibalism serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Rewrites "
"some sections of your brain to cause you to both crave and get an increase "
"in dopamine production when eating your own kind."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會重寫你大腦的某些部分，使你在食用同類時產生渴望並增加多巴胺的分泌。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Psychopathy serum"
msgid_plural "Psychopathy serums"
msgstr[0] "精神病血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Psychopathy serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Removes "
"your capacity to care about moralistic actions and morality in general."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會移除你對道德行為和一般道德觀念的關注能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Killer drive serum"
msgid_plural "Killer drive serums"
msgstr[0] "殺戮驅動血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Killer drive serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Heightens "
"dopamine production when killing something and as a result of that makes you"
" crave it."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會在你殺死某物時提高多巴胺的分泌，並因此讓你對此產生渴望。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Weak scent serum"
msgid_plural "Weak scent serums"
msgstr[0] "微弱氣味血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Weak scent serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Removes "
"most of your odour-producing sweat glands and general smelliness."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。它會移除你大部分產生氣味的汗腺和一般體味。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Prettification serum"
msgid_plural "Prettification serums"
msgstr[0] "美化血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Prettification serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Like "
"beauty creams, except you inject this one, and it actually works. Makes you "
"more appealing to look at."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。類似於美容霜，但這是注射用的，而且確實有效。讓你看起來更具吸引力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Heavy sleeper serum"
msgid_plural "Heavy sleeper serums"
msgstr[0] "沉睡者血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Heavy sleeper serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Lowers "
"your environmental reactivity while asleep."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。降低你睡眠時對環境的反應性。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Albinism serum"
msgid_plural "Albinism serums"
msgstr[0] "白化病血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Albinism serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Removes "
"the pigmentation from your body and removes your body's capability to "
"produce pigmentation."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。移除你身體的色素沉著，並消除身體產生色素的能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Rough skin serum"
msgid_plural "Rough skin serums"
msgstr[0] "粗糙皮膚血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Rough skin serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives your"
" skin a rough texture."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。賦予你的皮膚粗糙的質地。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "High nightvision serum"
msgid_plural "High nightvision serums"
msgstr[0] "高夜視血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'High nightvision serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"the amount of light-sensitive cones in your eyes to enable very good "
"nightvision."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。增加你眼睛中對光敏感的視錐細胞數量，以實現非常好的夜視能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Full nightvision serum"
msgid_plural "Full nightvision serums"
msgstr[0] "完全夜視血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Full nightvision serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
"an abundance of light-sensitive cones in your eyes, granting better "
"nightsight than most creatures have."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。賦予你眼睛中豐富的對光敏感的視錐細胞，提供比大多數生物更好的夜視能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Cephalopod eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Cephalopod eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "頭足類眼睛血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cephalopod eyes serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Mutates "
"your eye structure into that of a cephalopod."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。將你的眼睛結構突變為頭足類動物的眼睛。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Fey eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Fey eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "精靈眼睛血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fey eyes serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Replaces "
"the pigmentation of your eyes with self-modulating chromatophores that can "
"only shift into various shades of green."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。用只能轉變為各種綠色色調的自調節色素細胞替換你眼睛的色素沉著。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Feline eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Feline eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "貓眼血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Feline eyes serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Mutates "
"your eyes into those of a cat. Nightvision not included."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。將你的眼睛突變為貓的眼睛。不包含夜視能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Bird eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Bird eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "鳥眼血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bird eyes serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. "
"Structurally changes your eyes to be similar to that of avians, heightening "
"visual acuity and perception."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。結構上改變你的眼睛，使其類似於鳥類，提高視覺敏銳度和感知能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Infrared vision serum"
msgid_plural "Infrared vision serums"
msgstr[0] "紅外視覺血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Infrared vision serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Changes "
"your eyes to see the infrared wavelengths, allowing you to see warm-blooded "
"creatures in the dark."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。改變你的眼睛以看到紅外波長，讓你能在黑暗中看到溫血生物。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Lizard eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Lizard eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "蜥蜴眼睛血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lizard eyes serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. "
"Structurally mutates your eyes to be like a reptile's. Reptilian infrared "
"not included."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。結構上突變你的眼睛，使其類似於爬行動物的眼睛。不包含爬行動物的紅外視覺。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Lizard infrared serum"
msgid_plural "Lizard infrared serums"
msgstr[0] "蜥蜴紅外血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lizard infrared serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Grants "
"your eyes the ability to see into the infrared spectrum like various "
"reptiles, physical changes may apply."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。賦予你的眼睛像各種爬行動物一樣看到紅外光譜的能力，可能會伴隨物理變化。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Very fast healer serum"
msgid_plural "Very fast healer serums"
msgstr[0] "極速癒合血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Very fast healer serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"cell division rate in response to structural damage, improving your healing "
"factor above normal."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。提高細胞對結構損傷的分裂速率，將你的癒合因子提升至正常水平以上。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Regeneration serum"
msgid_plural "Regeneration serums"
msgstr[0] "再生血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Regeneration serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Cell "
"division rate in response to structural damage is increased to nearly "
"unnatural levels, improving healing to a very high degree."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。細胞對結構損傷的分裂速率提高到近乎非自然的水平，將癒合能力提升到非常高的程度。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Reptilian healing serum"
msgid_plural "Reptilian healing serums"
msgstr[0] "爬行類癒合血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reptilian healing serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Grants "
"self-setting and automatic fast repair to both skeletal breakage and wounds "
"of the flesh."
msgstr "一種特殊的誘變血清，旨在賦予你單一突變。提供骨骼斷裂與肉體傷口的自我復位與自動快速修復能力。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Very little sleep serum"
msgid_plural "Very little sleep serums"
msgstr[0] "極微睡眠血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Very little sleep serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Allows "
"your brain to perform short bursts of functions similar to REM sleep while "
"awake, lengthening times you're awake and lowering the amount of time you "
"need to sleep."
